@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy";
}

<div class="container my-5">
    <h1 class="text-success text-center mb-4">@ViewData["Title"]</h1>

    <div class="card shadow-sm border-0">
        <div class="card-body">
            <p>
                At <strong>Avondale Islamic Centre</strong>, we are committed to protecting your privacy and ensuring the security of the personal information you share with us through this website.
                As part of our effort to provide a smooth and safe experience — especially for school registrations, class bookings, and donations — we collect certain personal information from you.
            </p>

            <h5 class="text-success mt-4">What We Collect</h5>
            <p>We may collect the following information from you:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Your name</li>
                <li>Contact information (email address, phone number)</li>
                <li>Your location</li>
                <li>Billing or purchase information (for donations or hall bookings)</li>
            </ul>

            <h5 class="text-success mt-4">Why We Collect It</h5>
            <p>
                We collect this information to ensure our school and mosque services run smoothly and securely. This helps us contact you when necessary, confirm bookings or registrations, and keep our records up to date.
                For example, if your child is enrolled in a class and we need to urgently reach you, having accurate contact details is vital.
            </p>

            <h5 class="text-success mt-4">Your Rights</h5>
            <p>
                Providing some information is optional. However, if you choose not to provide your contact details, we may not be able to reach you in case of important updates or emergencies.
            </p>
            <p>
                You have the right to request a copy of any personal information we hold about you, and you may ask us to correct it if you believe it is inaccurate.
                If you would like to request or correct your personal data, please contact us at:
            </p>

            <p class="mb-0"><strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:admin@aic.com">admin@aic.com</a></p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
